Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.03,0:00:02.10,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,By January 1986, the\NSpace Shuttle had
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.10,0:00:04.16,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,flown twenty-four\Ntimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.12,0:00:06.88,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,Each flight\Nreinforced one idea —
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.92,0:00:08.36,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,the system worked.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.37,0:00:11.04,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,Across those\Nflights, engineers
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.04,0:00:12.71,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,documented O-ring\Ndamage.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.49,0:00:15.71,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,Erosion, blow-by —\Nhot gas past seals
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.71,0:00:17.92,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,designed to hold.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.76,0:00:20.10,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,Low-temperature\Nflights all showed
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.10,0:00:21.45,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,distress.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.43,0:00:23.25,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,But each flight\Nsurvived, and the
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.25,0:00:25.07,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,warning lost force.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.16,0:00:27.74,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,Danger became a\Nknown condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.48,0:00:30.38,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,A stop signal became\Na line item.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.42,0:00:33.19,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,The night before\NChallenger, engineers
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.19,0:00:34.95,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,recommended against\Nlaunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.95,0:00:36.98,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,The burden shifted —
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.03,0:00:38.83,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,instead of proving\Nit safe to fly,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.83,0:00:40.63,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,they were asked to\Nprove it was
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.63,0:00:42.42,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,unsafe.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.42,0:00:45.31,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,On the coldest\Nmorning the program had
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.31,0:00:47.20,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,ever faced,\Nseventy-three seconds was
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.20,0:00:49.09,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,all the physics\Nneeded.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.15,0:00:51.35,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,The warning was\Nnever missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.30,0:00:53.23,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,It had been made\Nsurvivable for too
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.23,0:00:54.16,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,long.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.94,0:00:57.53,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,Small causes,\Nmassive consequences.
